CROW et al., Appellants, v. COFFIN et al., Respondents. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. March 16, 1894.) Action by Moses R. Crow and another against William E. Coffin and others.

Argued before VAN BRUNT, P. X, and FOLLETT and PARKER, JX

No opinion. Motion granted, with $10 costs.
